comment: Oladipo (ORL) makes contact with Williams' (DAL) arms and affects his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Nowitzki (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Felton (DAL) and Gordon (ORL) briefly engage and separate while attempting to establish post position.
Williams (DAL) and Gordon (ORL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Gordon (ORL) maintains legal guarding position without making contact with the ball and Pachulia (DAL) is correctly called for the traveling violation. Any contact on the
Payton (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly knocks the ball away from Williams (DAL).
Payton (ORL) maintains his pivot foot.
Pachulia (DAL) sets the screen on Gordon (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gordon (ORL) legally contests Nowitzki's (DAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with the jump ball prior to it reaching its apex.
Williams (DAL) sets the screen on Gordon (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Pachulia (DAL) is the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB. Since the play does not occur in the last two minutes, it cannot be reviewed.
Vucevic (ORL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Pachulia (DAL) that affects his shot attempt.
Pachulia (DAL) and Nowitzki (DAL) maintain legal guarding position as they contest Gordon's (ORL) layup attempt.
Gordon (ORL) makes contact with Pachulia (DAL) that causes him to fall to the floor after he secures the rebound.
Pachulia (DAL) sets the screen on Oladipo (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact with Parsons (DAL) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Parsons (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LHH shows that Pachulia (DAL) makes contact with Vucevic's (ORL) arm that affects his shot attempt prior to the blocked shot by Parsons (DAL).
Jennings (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Williams (DAL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Fournier (ORL) pushes the airborne Pachulia (DAL) and the contact affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) makes contact with Matthews' (DAL) body and head that affects his shot attempt.
Pachulia (DAL) firms up as he sets the screen on Fournier (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Oladipo (ORL) does not have part of his hand underneath the ball when he brings it to a pause and continues his dribble.
Vucevic (ORL) cleanly blocks Williams' (DAL) driving shot attempt.
Nowitzki (DAL) makes body to body contact with Gordon (ORL) that affects his RSBQ.
Pachulia (DAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Vucevic's (ORL) drive and shot attempt.
Matthews (DAL) commits a take foul on Jennings (ORL).
